   <head>
      <hi>In Thomae Nicholai occidenta<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>lem</hi> Jndiam St. Gosson.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>SOrdescant Croesi radiantia tecta Pyrope,</l>
      <l>Et iaceat rutili pompa superba Mydae.</l>
      <l>Aurea foelici voluuntur secula cursu,</l>
      <l>Pactôli assiduè flumina verae tument.</l>
      <l>Terra ferax pandit, sua viscera plena metallis</l>
      <l>Praegnans, diuitias parturit illa suas.</l>
      <l>India luxuriat, locupleti prole triumphat,</l>
      <l>Pingue solum gemmis, fundere gestit opes.</l>
      <l>O vos qui patriae cupitis fulci<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>e ru<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="2 letters">
            <desc>••</desc>
         </gap>am,</l>
      <l>Et dare mella bonis
<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>urea, mentis
<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>p<gap reason="illegible" resp="#pdcc" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>.</l>
      <l>Cortezi hos animo cupidè lustrate labores,</l>
      <l>Post{que}, reluctanti credite vela Salo.</l>
